description.description:
Adds support for Astar, an interoperable blockchain platform for Polkadot and Ethereum ecosystems supporting both Wasm and EVM smart contracts.

After installing the Snap, visit the Astar Portal at https://portal.astar.network/ to connect. Make sure to select 'Astar Snap' under the Native Accounts options.
